overview.en: VBT Token is a digital asset issued by VBT trading platform which referred to as VBT. It's the certificate of interest in the VBT platform ecology. People who hold VBT can Enjoy a series of rights and interests, such as asset value-added, interest-generating through lock-in, mortgage lending and voting supervision.
overview.zh: VBT Token是由VBT交易平台发行的数字资产，简称VBT。VBT是VBT平台生态的权益凭证，持有VBT的用户可享受资产增值、锁仓生息、抵押借贷、投票监督等系列权益。
